@startuml uml_class_media
title LLD — media-service (HTTP + gRPC — proto/media.proto)
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica

package "HTTP / gRPC transport" {
  class "Signed-URL HTTP API\n(server.ts)" as Http <<Node>>
  class "MediaService\n(grpc-server.ts)" as Grpc <<Node>> {
    CreateUploadUrl()
    CompleteUpload()
    GetDownloadUrl()
  }
}

package "Application" {
  class "Media metadata\n+ policy" as D <<service>>
}

package "Infrastructure" {
  class "Metadata DB\n(Prisma)" as R <<repository>>
  class "Object store\n(S3 / MinIO)" as O
}

Http --> D
Grpc --> D
D --> R
D --> O

note bottom of Grpc
  **Contract:** `proto/media.proto`
  — **no** file bytes on gRPC; client
  uploads directly to object storage
  using returned signed URLs.
end note

@enduml
